description: [PR Newswire] - CALGARY, Jan. 5, 2017 /CNW/ - Whitecap Resources Inc. ("Whitecap" or the "Company") (WCP.TO) is pleased to announce that it has closed an issuance of Cdn$200 million senior secured notes which have an annual coupon rate of 3.46% and mature on January 5, 2022. The notes were issued by way of a private placement, pursuant to a note purchase and private shelf agreement, and rank equally with Whitecap's obligations under its bank facilities. Proceeds from the notes will be used to repay a portion of Whitecap's outstanding bank debt.
